window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Claire Benolt doesn’t believe in weird stuff.</p> <p>Ghosts, vampires, and werewolves just aren’t real. At least that’s what she thought. Determined to leave her murky past behind, Claire gladly accepts a job working with a private detective. There’s only one catch. Her new boss just happens to be a vampire, and he wants her help catching the serial killer terrorizing New Orleans. And then there’s Mason, the hot Nightwalker who wants to eat her up, in more than one way.</p> <p>Can she survive the Ripper of New Orleans and Mason?</p> <p><b>Dark Side Mysteries:</b></p> <p></p> <ol> <li><i>Flirting with Disaster</i></li> <li><i>A Walk on the Dark Side</i></li> <li><i>Witchy Business</i></li> </ol>"; 
